    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Shougalo Miss</placeName>
                <date>26 May 1857</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <sic>
                    <addressee>Mr Lezer</addressee>
                </sic>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Kind sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">Your esteemed favour<lb/> of the <date>4th</date> instant has come
                duly to hand.</p>
            <p>I am happy to learn of your forming a new Congregation<lb/> of which you and the
                ministers and trust that success<lb/> may Crown your noble efforts in behalf of
                the<lb/> religion of my fathers. As for a loan<lb/> I am unable to grant and being
                reduced in<lb/> circumstances nor could I <del>
                    <add>?</add>
                </del> influence any<lb/> loan from others as there are but <hi rend="underline"
                    >five</hi> Jews<lb/> in the state of <placeName>Mississippi</placeName> only one
                or<lb/> two in a place scattered through the lands.<lb/> Your occident has only been
                coming since<lb/>
                <date>1853</date> continuing in <date>August</date> so that I<lb/> do not owe but
                    <del>ow</del> four years subscriptions.<lb/> one of my nephews will go out
                    <placeName>north</placeName><lb/> this summer and settle with you.</p>
            <p>I am now over eighty years of age<lb/> youth and manhood have both given<lb/> way the
                gray cold feelings of <sic>lifes</sic> decline,<lb/> and the only pleasures now left
                me are my<lb/> my daily devotions and religious exercises.<lb/> With best wishes for
                your health and prosperity</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I am very truly yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <persName role="author">Solomon Soher</persName>
            </p>
            <p>see next page.</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p><sic>youre</sic> occident has been directed to<lb/>
                <persName>Mr Koppert</persName> but I have been<lb/> taking it. So you will please
                change<lb/> the Address to <persName role="author">Solomon Soher</persName></p>
        </body>
